---
title: Venison, Beef & Bacon Bolognese Filo Pie  with Portabello Mushrooms
description: When you don’t know what to eat, a pie is a sure-fire way to solve the problem. Classic bolognese flavours are cooked
up in a beef and venison sauce with hidden mushrooms to add the comfort factor every pie needs. You can relax now
that all your dinner time questions have been answered.
